Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
clinic.Appointment
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Appointment>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Imaging
public class Appointment extends Object implements Comparable<Appointment>
Represents an appointment in a clinic system, storing information such as the date, timeslot, patient profile, and provider information.
